title: Stephen Hawking's Cambridge funeral
text:
Stephen Hawking's Cambridge funeral Saturday, March 31, 2018 - 00:43 
Well-wishers filled the streets of Cambridge, England for the funeral of legendary physicist Stephen Hawking, with celebrities joining his family at the private ceremony.Rough cut
